KTHena mock inference images (vllm-mock, sglang-mock)
=====================================================

These container images and their Python sources were derived from the
AIBrix project development mock application:
  https://github.com/vllm-project/aibrix (development/app)

Upstream attributions
---------------------

* vLLM (OpenAI-compatible HTTP API and Prometheus metric naming):
  https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm
  Copyright The vLLM contributors. Licensed under Apache License 2.0.

* SGLang (Prometheus metrics conventions):
  https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang
  Copyright The SGLang Team. Licensed under Apache License 2.0.

The mock implementations are not forks of vLLM or SGLang; they provide
compatible endpoints and metric names for testing and development.
